{
  "page": "List of characters created for the Telltale game",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>This page lists the characters that have been created for <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_A_Telltale_Games_Series\" title=\"Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series\">Game of Thrones - A Telltale Games Series</a></i>, a video game based on the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, and have no equivalent counterpart in the books. The characters are listed according to their first appearance or mention in the game.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Season_1\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Season 1</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Episode_1:_Iron_From_Ice\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 1: Iron From Ice</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Episode_2:_The_Lost_Lords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 2: The Lost Lords</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Episode_3:_The_Sword_in_the_Darkness\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 3: The Sword in the Darkness</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Episode_4:_Sons_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 4: Sons of Winter</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Episode_5:_A_Nest_of_Vipers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 5: A Nest of Vipers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Episode_6:_The_Ice_Dragon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Episode 6: The Ice Dragon</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Season_1\">Season 1</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_game&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Season 1\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Episode_1:_Iron_From_Ice\">Episode 1: Iron From Ice</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_game&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Episode 1: Iron From Ice\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Gared Tuttle, played by Daniel Kendrick. He is the squire of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li>Norren, played by Geoffrey Leesley. He is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Forrester\" title=\"House Forrester\">Forrester</a> man-at-arms.</li>\n<li>Bowen, played by Matt Mercer. He is Norren's squire.</li>\n<li>Thermund, played by JB Blanc. He is the Lord's Sentinel to Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li>Errold, a Forrester man-at-arms.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Gregor Forrester, played by Robin Atkin-Downes. He is the Lord of Ironrath and head of House Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Talia Forrester, played by Molly Stone. She is the daughter of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ryon Forrester, played by Louis Suc. He is the son of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Mira Forrester, played by Martha Mackintosh. She is the daughter of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Rodrik Forrester, played by Russ Bain. He is the son of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady Elissa Forrester, née Branfield, played by Lara Pulver. She is the wife of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ethan Forrester, played by Christopher Nelson. He is the son of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li>Malcolm Branfield, played by JB Blanc. He is the brother of Elissa Forrester.</li>\n<li>Duncan Tuttle, played by Robin Atkin-Downes. He is the uncle of Gared Tuttle and the <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of Ironrath.</li>\n<li>Ser Royland Degore, played by Brian George. He is the <a href=\"/index.php/Master-at-arms\" title=\"Master-at-arms\">master-at-arms</a> at Ironrath.</li>\n<li>Erik, played by Yuri Lowenthal. He is a thief at Ironrath.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Maester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/15px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/23px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/30px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Maester Ortengryn, played by David Franklin. He is the <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> at Ironrath.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Ludd Whitehill, played by Geoffrey Leesley. He is the Lord of Highpoint and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Whitehill\" title=\"House Whitehill\">House Whitehill</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Gryff Whitehill, played by Sacha Dhawan. He is the son of Ludd Whitehill.</li>\n<li>Britt Warrick, played by Alistair James. He is a Whitehill man-at-arms.</li>\n<li>Sera Durwell, played by Natasha Loring. She is a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">bastard</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a>, and her real name is Sera Flowers.</li>\n<li>Tom, played by Yuri Lowenthal. He is a servant in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Gerhard Forrester, known as Gerhard the Tall. He was the founder of House Forrester. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Cedric Forrester, the builder of Ironrath. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Thorren Forrester, known as Thorren the Bold. He was the father of Gregor Forrester. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Episode_2:_The_Lost_Lords\">Episode 2: The Lost Lords</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_game&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Episode 2: The Lost Lords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Forrester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Forrester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/15px-House_Forrester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/23px-House_Forrester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Forrester.svg/30px-House_Forrester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Asher Forrester, played by Alex Jordan. He is the exiled son of Gregor Forrester.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Meereen.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/15px-Meereen.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/23px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/30px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a> Beskha the Basilisk, played by Toks Olagundoye. She is a sellsword in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.</li>\n<li>Tazal, played by Brian George. He is a commander of the Lost Legion.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Gwyn Whitehill, played by Laura Bailey. She is the daughter of Ludd Whitehill.</li>\n<li>Elaena Glenmore, played by Amy Pemberton. She is the sister of Arthur Glenmore.</li>\n<li>Arthur Glenmore, played by Matt Littler. He is the brother of Elaena Glenmore.</li>\n<li>Lucan, played by Fabio Tassone and later Matt Wolf. He is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> man-at-arms.</li>\n<li>Damien, played by Owen Thomas. He is a Lannister man-at-arms.</li>\n<li>Lord Rickard Morgryn, played by Oliver Vaquer and later Nick Afka Thomas. He is a merchant lord in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord Andros, played by Robin Atkin Downes. He is a merchant lord in King's Landing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Denner Frostfinger, played by Jeremy Crutchley. He is an officer of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Finn, played by Yuri Lowenthal. He is a ranger of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Owyn Cotter, played by Joseph Balderamma. He is a builder of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li>Lord Glenmore, the head of House Glenmore. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Lady Glenmore, Lord Glenmore's wife. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Lord Branfield, the father of Elissa Forrester. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Lady Talia Branfield, Lord Branfield's wife. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Casper, played by JB Blanc. He is a recruit of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Meereen.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/15px-Meereen.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/23px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/30px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a> Bezzaq, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Masters\" title=\"Great Masters\">Great Masters</a> of Meereen.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Episode_3:_The_Sword_in_the_Darkness\">Episode 3: The Sword in the Darkness</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_game&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Episode 3: The Sword in the Darkness\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Harys, played by Ron Bottitta. He is a Whitehill man-at-arms.</li>\n<li>Lord Garibald Tarwick, played by Rob Rackstraw. He is the head of House Tarwick.</li>\n<li>Croft, played by Adam Leadbeater. He is the leader of the Hellhounds.</li>\n<li>Old Rob, a farmer in the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a>. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Namond, an inhabitant of Old Rob's farm. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Meghan, an inhabitant of Old Rob's farm. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li>Fegg, played by Matthew Mercer. He is a wagon driver in the wolfswood.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Hugh, a ranger of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lobor, a steward of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Errold Holt, a recruit of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Wells_(North).svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Wells (North).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Wells_%28North%29.svg/15px-House_Wells_%28North%29.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c0/House_Wells_%28North%29.svg/23px-House_Wells_%28North%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c0/House_Wells_%28North%29.svg/30px-House_Wells_%28North%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Corlys Wells, a recruit of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Wendel, a member of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Night%27s_Watch.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/15px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/23px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Duff, a member of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Second_Sons.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Second Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/15px-Second_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/23px-Second_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/30px-Second_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Jodan, a sellsword of the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Sons\" title=\"Second Sons\">Second Sons</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Second_Sons.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Second Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/15px-Second_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/23px-Second_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/30px-Second_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Therrond, a sellsword of the Second Sons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Second_Sons.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Second Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/15px-Second_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/23px-Second_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/30px-Second_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Kieran, a sellsword of the Second Sons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Second_Sons.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Second Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/15px-Second_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/23px-Second_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fa/Second_Sons.svg/30px-Second_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Penn, a sellsword of the Second Sons.</li>\n<li>Rhogar, a member of the Lost Legion.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Episode_4:_Sons_of_Winter\">Episode 4: Sons of Winter</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_game&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Episode 4: Sons of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Lannister.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/15px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/23px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lyman Lannister, played by Carl Prekopp. He is a third cousin to <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a>.</li>\n<li>Sylvi, played by Clare Louise Connolly. She is a <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">wildling</a> and the sister of Owyn Cotter.</li>\n<li>Nancy, a wildling <a href=\"/index.php/Spearwife\" title=\"Spearwife\">spearwife</a>.</li>\n<li>Barbara, a wildling spearwife.</li>\n<li>Jane, a wildling spearwife.</li>\n<li>Rose, a wildling spearwife.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/File:Maester.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/15px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/23px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/30px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ebbert Whitehill, a novice or acolyte at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Torrhen Whitehill, Ludd Whitehill's heir. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady Whitehill, Ludd Whitehill's wife. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Whitehill.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Whitehill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/15px-House_Whitehill.svg.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/23px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3a/House_Whitehill.svg/30px-House_Whitehill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Karl Whitehill, a son of Ludd Whitehill who died of <a href=\"/index.php/Greyscale\" title=\"Greyscale\">greyscale</a>. <small>(mentioned only)</small></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:Meereen.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Meereen.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/15px-Meereen.png\" width=\"15\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/23px-Meereen.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/Meereen.png/30px-Meereen.png 2x\" /></a> Dezhor zo Raza, one of the Great Masters of Meereen.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Episode_5:_A_Nest_of_Vipers\">Episode 5: A Nest of Vipers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_characters_created_for_the_Telltale_ga